### AIPLAN Course Meeting Locations

The <a href="http://secondlife.com">Second Life</a> virtual world allows 
you to obtain a free avatar and meet with others and communicate via text chat,
instant messaging and voice.

You can try to go to one "primary" meeting area initially as show below.
If that is full try an alternative "backup" location from the list below in the
Virtual University of Edinburgh (Vue) regions in Second
Life. Communication is possible using group text and voice chat
wherever you are located in Second Life. So, you might also suggest
alternative "popup" areas to meet in smaller groups, or with others you
interact or study with.  Perhaps suggest an area for those who speak
your own language or who are in your own time zone as a regular
meeting place.

