### IRC Internet Relay Chat

You can join the AIPLAN IRC channel by clicking the link:

<a href="http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=aiplan">http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=aiplan</a>

More experienced IRC users can connect to the server with the next information:

* Server: irc.freenode.net
* Port: 6667 (Default)
* Channel: #aiplan

### Skype

* Skype group to discuss video lectures, and other AI material.
* Feel free to join by adding this account on Skype: alejandro.lucena
* If you choose to join the group, please include in the request that you wish to be part of the study group (for organizational purposes)
* Invitations that lack anything along the lines of "I wish to be part of the study group" will not be accepted

